{\displaystyle \mathrm {r} _{1}={\begin{bmatrix}\cos {2\pi  \over n}&-\sin {2\pi  \over n}\\[8pt]\sin {2\pi  \over n}&\cos {2\pi  \over n}\end{bmatrix}}\qquad \mathrm {s} _{0}={\begin{bmatrix}1&0\\0&-1\end{bmatrix}}}



