 number of normal subgroups of order 2 (must be 1, 3, 7, or 15) (by (4)) 
 number of subgroups of order 4 (must be odd) 
 number of normal subgroups of order 4 (must be odd) 
 number of subgroups of order 8 (must be 1, 3, 7, or 15) (see (2) and (3)) 
 number of normal subgroups of order 8 (must equal preceding column by (2))


